---
layout: base.njk
title: "Wellness & Fitness Gear Reviews"
description: "Home gym equipment, ergonomic tools, standing desks, and recovery gear — reviews that help you stay active, comfortable, and healthy while working from home."
permalink: /wellness/index.html
---
<section class="section">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <h1 class="section-title">Wellness &amp; Fitness</h1>
    <p class="section-subtitle">Home gym equipment, standing desks, ergonomic chairs, and recovery gear — everything that keeps you moving and feeling good.</p>
    <div class="article-grid">
      {% for article in collections.wellnessArticles %}
      <article class="article-card">
        <div class="card-body">
          <span class="card-category">{{ article.data.category | categoryLabel }}</span>
          <a href="{{ article.url | url }}" style="display:block">
            <h2 class="card-title">{{ article.data.title }}</h2>
          </a>
          <p class="card-excerpt">{{ article.data.description | truncate(120) }}</p>
          <div class="card-meta">
            <span>{{ article.date | postDate }}</span>
          </div>
          <a href="{{ article.url | url }}" class="read-more" style="margin-top:0.75rem;display:inline-flex">Read guide →</a>
        </div>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
